  "title": "HR & Marketing Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Are you energetic, people-focused, and passionate about connecting talent with opportunity? Octomate Staffing is part of HRnetGroup, blending recruitment expertise with marketing and HR innovation. This role gives you exposure across people operations and brand engagement.</p><p><strong>Learning opportunities:</strong></p><ul><li>Dual exposure to HR operations and marketing projects</li><li>Assist in the entire recruitment process </li><li>Stay updated with market trends and employer branding strategies </li></ul><p><strong>Job description:</strong></p><ul><li>Screen resumes and conduct interviews</li><li>Take part in exciting hiring projects</li><li>Create digital and social media content </li></ul><p><strong>Who we are looking for:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in design software and video editing tools</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced envrionment</li><li>Team player with good communication and coordination skills</li><li>Able to commit for minimally 3 months</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul><p>Work location: Orchard<br />Working Schedule: Monday – Friday, 8.30am – 5.30pm<br />*We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
